<!-- What -->
<h1 style="margin-top:20px"><strong class="pulse">Pulse</strong> <em class="keyword">continuous integration server</em></h1>

<div id="pwhat" class="grid_7 alpha">
  <p>
    <strong class="pulse">Pulse</strong> is a <em class="keyword">continuous integration server</em>:
    it builds your code on every change and notifies you of the results.
  <p>
    <strong class="pulse">Pulse</strong> is <em>simple</em> to set up and use.</p>
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong class="pulse">Pulse</strong> supports <em>advanced</em> features including
    <a title="power :: feature tour :: pulse continuous integration server"
       href="features/tour/power/">distributed builds</a>,
    <a title="power :: feature tour :: pulse continuous integration server"
       href="features/tour/power/">personal builds</a>,
    and a unique <a title="maintainability :: feature tour :: pulse continuous integration server"
                    href="features/tour/maintainability/">templated</a> configuration system.</p>
  </p>
</div>

<div class="grid_8 push_half omega">
